       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    ARI43104.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA ARI43104.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Gest瓊o de Perfil
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE ARI43104         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD2000 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD3000 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01 WS-SQL-AUXILIARY.
         05 IND-NULL                       PIC S9(04) BINARY.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY ARCV4310.
       COPY ARCV4311.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0010.
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY ARCK0001.
       COPY ARCK0002.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-ARVT3000 PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARVT3000'.
           05 CON-ARVT2000 PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARVT2000'.
           05 WS-PROGNAME  PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARI43104'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-COUNT         PIC S9(06) VALUE ZEROES.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE ARI43104         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO ARCV4310-MSG.
           MOVE ARCV4310-ASE               TO ARCV4311-ASE.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ARCV4310-ADE               TO ARCV4311-ADE.

           PERFORM 2100-VALIDACOES
              THRU 2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-INSERE-DADOS
                 THRU 2299-INSERE-DADOS-EXIT
           END-iF
           .
       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-VALIDACOES.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-VALIDACOES' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
      *    Valida誽o de m嫞imo de perfis inibida em desenvolvimento
      *
      *    PERFORM 2110-VALIDA-MAX-PERFIS
      *       THRU 2110-VALIDA-MAX-PERFIS-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2120-VALIDA-PERFIL
                 THRU 2120-VALIDA-PERFIL-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
       2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2110-VALIDA-MAX-PERFIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2110-VALIDA-MAX-PERFIS.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2110-VALIDA-MAX-PERFIS'   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ARCV4310-GUSERNAME
             TO ARCD3000-GUSERNAME

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT COUNT(*)
                 INTO   :WS-COUNT
                 FROM ARVT3000_PERFISUSER
                 WHERE
                    UPPER (GUSERNAME) = UPPER (:ARCD3000-GUSERNAME)
           END-EXEC


           MOVE CON-ARVT3000
             TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 IF WS-COUNT >= ARCK0002-MAX-PERFIS
                   MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                     TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                   MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                     TO ARCV4311-GUSERNAME-S
                   MOVE ARCK0001-MAX-PERFIS
                     TO ARCV4311-GUSERNAME-MSG
                 END-IF
              ELSE
                 IF NOT VIAL0001-CRIACAO
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO ARCV4311-GUSERNAME-S
                    MOVE ARCK0001-GUSERNAME-N-EXISTS
                      TO ARCV4311-GUSERNAME-MSG
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
       2110-VALIDA-MAX-PERFIS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2120-VALIDA-PERFIL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2120-VALIDA-PERFIL.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2120-VALIDA-PERFIL'   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

                 MOVE ARCV4310-CPERFIL
                   TO ARCD2000-CPERFIL

                 EXEC SQL
                    SELECT CPERFIL
                         , INDPERM
                    INTO  :ARCD2000-CPERFIL
                         ,:ARCD2000-INDPERM
                    FROM ARVT2002_INFPERFIL
                    WHERE CPERFIL = :ARCD2000-CPERFIL
                 END-EXEC

                 MOVE CON-ARVT2000
                   TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME

                 PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
                    THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT

                 IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                    IF NOT DB2-OK
                       MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                         TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                       MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                         TO ARCV4311-CPERFIL-S
                       MOVE ARCK0001-CPERFIL-N-EXISTS
                         TO ARCV4311-CPERFIL-MSG
                    END-IF
                    IF DB2-OK
                       IF ARCD2000-INDPERM   EQUAL 'N'
                          CONTINUE
                       ELSE
                          MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                            TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                          MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                            TO ARCV4311-CPERFIL-S
                          MOVE ARCK0001-ESTE-PER-AESTEUSER-N
                            TO ARCV4311-CPERFIL-MSG
                       END-IF
                    END-IF
                 END-IF.
      *
       2120-VALIDA-PERFIL-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2200-INSERE-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-INSERE-DADOS.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2200-INSERE-DADOS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ARCV4310-GUSERNAME
             TO ARCD3000-GUSERNAME
           MOVE ARCV4310-CPERFIL
             TO ARCD3000-CPERFIL
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I
             TO ARCD3000-CUSERID


           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS

           EXEC SQL
                 INSERT INTO
                ARVT3000_PERFISUSER
                (
                   GUSERNAME
                 , CPERFIL
                 , CUSERID
                 , HTIMEST
                )
                VALUES (
                       :ARCD3000-GUSERNAME
                     , :ARCD3000-CPERFIL
                     , :ARCD3000-CUSERID
                     , CURRENT TIMESTAMP
                )
           END-EXEC


              MOVE CON-ARVT3000               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME

              PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
                 THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT

              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 IF DB2-DUPREC
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                      MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                        TO ARCV4311-GUSERNAME-S
                      MOVE ARCK0001-GUSERNAME-A-EXISTS
                        TO ARCV4311-GUSERNAME-MSG
                      MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                        TO ARCV4311-CPERFIL-S
                      MOVE ARCK0001-CPERFIL-A-EXISTS
                        TO ARCV4311-CPERFIL-MSG
                 ELSE
                    IF NOT DB2-OK
                       MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                         TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                       MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                         TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
                    END-IF
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF


           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                        CONTINUE
           END-IF
           .

       2299-INSERE-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.


      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ARCV4311-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE ARCV4311-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE ARCV4311-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.


       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0010.
           COPY VIAP0016.
